  <brief_title>Glycemic Durability After Metformin Failure</brief_title>
  <acronym>AMAZING</acronym>
  <official_title>Effect of Glimepiride, Vildagliptin, Pioglitazone and Canagliflozin on Durability of Glycemic Control After Metformin Failure in Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
